# TC18: LowBatteryCleared1
# Precondition: LowBatteryMode, charging is in progress and battery recovers above safe threshold
# Action: battery level becomes higher than the low-battery threshold during charging
# Expected: StandbyMode
power
battery 5
low-battery
expect power on
expect mode LowBatteryMode
expect battery 5
expect motor stopped
expect cleaner off
charge
expect power on
expect charging on
expect battery 15
expect mode StandbyMode
expect motor stopped
expect cleaner off
expect cleanerMode off
exit
